query: SELECT op.id, op.strategyId, s.name as strategyName, op.direction, op.quantity, op.entryPrice, op.entryTime, op.isTest FROM open_positions op LEFT JOIN strategies s ON op.strategyId = s.id ORDER BY op.entryTime DESC;
